&lt;samp&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/script\"><code>&lt;script&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/shadow\"><code>&lt;shadow&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/slot\"><code>&lt;slot&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/small\"><code>&lt;small&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/source\"><code>&lt;source&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"nonStdElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/spacer\"><code>&lt;spacer&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement deprecatedElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strike\"><code>&lt;strike&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><strong>HTML 공개 요약 요소</strong> (<strong><code>&lt;요약&gt;</code></strong>) 요소는 (\"상세\") 요소의 공개 상자에 대한 요약, 캡션 또는 범례를 지정한다. </span> <code>&lt;요약&gt;</code> 요소를 클릭하면 부모 <code>&lt;상세&gt;</code> 요소의 상태가 열리거나 닫힌다.</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"375\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/tabbed/summary.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>\n\n<p class=\"hidden\">The source for this interactive example is stored in a GitHub repository. If you'd like to contribute to the interactive examples project, please clone <a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/interactive-examples\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">https://github.com/mdn/interactive-examples </a> and send us a pull request.</p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Permitted content</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\">Phrasing content</a> or one element of <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#heading_content\">Heading content</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Tag omission</th>\n   <td>None, both the start tag and the end tag are mandatory.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Permitted parents</th>\n   <td>The <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/details\"><code>&lt;details&gt;</code></a> element.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Permitted ARIA roles</th>\n   <td><code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#button\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">button</a></code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">DOM interface</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attributes","title":"Attributes","isH3":false,"content":"<p>This element only includes the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\">global attributes</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"usage_notes","title":"Usage notes","isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <code>&lt;summary&gt;</code> element's contents can be any heading content, plain text, or HTML that can be used within a paragraph.</p>\n\n<p>A <code>&lt;summary&gt;</code> element may <em>only</em> be used as the first child of a <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> element. When the user clicks on the summary, the parent <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> element is toggled open or closed, and then a <code><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/Reference/Events/toggle\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">toggle</a></code> event is sent to the <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> element, which can be used to let you know when this state change occurs.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"default_label_text","title":"Default label text","isH3":true,"content":"<p>If a <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> element's first child is not a <code>&lt;summary&gt;</code> element, the <a href=\"/ko/docs/Glossary/User_agent\">user agent</a> will use a default string (typically \"Details\") as the label for the disclosure box.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"default_style","title":"Default style","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Per the HTML specification, the default style for <code>&lt;summary&gt;</code> elements includes <code>display: list-item</code>. This makes it possible to change or remove the icon displayed as the disclosure widget next to the label from the default, which is typically a triangle.</p>\n\n<p>You can also change the style to <code>display: block</code> to remove the disclosure triangle.</p>\n\n<p>See the <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Browser compatibility</a> section for details, as not all browsers support full functionality of this element yet.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Below are some examples showing <code>&lt;summary&gt;</code> in use. You can find more examples in the documentation for the <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/details\"><code>&lt;details&gt;</code></a> element.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"basic_example","title":"Basic example","isH3":true,"content":"<p>A simple example showing the use of <code>&lt;summary&gt;</code> in a <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/details\"><code>&lt;details&gt;</code></a> element:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>details</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">open</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>summary</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Overview<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>summary</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Cash on hand: $500.00<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Current invoice: $75.30<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Due date: 5/6/19<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>details</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Basic example sample\" id=\"frame_basic_example\" width=\"650\" height=\"120\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary/_sample_.basic_example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summaries_as_headings","title":"Summaries as headings","isH3":true,"content":"<p>You can use heading elements in <code>&lt;summary&gt;</code>, like this:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>details</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">open</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>summary</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Overview<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>summary</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Cash on hand: $500.00<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Current invoice: $75.30<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Due date: 5/6/19<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>details</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Summaries as headings sample\" id=\"frame_summaries_as_headings\" width=\"650\" height=\"120\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary/_sample_.summaries_as_headings.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>\n\n<p>This currently has some spacing issues that could be addressed using CSS.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html_in_summaries","title":"HTML in summaries","isH3":true,"content":"<p>This example adds some semantics to the <code>&lt;summary&gt;</code> element to indicate the label as important:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>details</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">open</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>summary</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>strong</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Overview<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>strong</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>summary</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Cash on hand: $500.00<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Current invoice: $75.30<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Due date: 5/6/19<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>details</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"HTML in summaries sample\" id=\"frame_html_in_summaries\" width=\"650\" height=\"120\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary/_sample_.html_in_summaries.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/interactive-elements.html#the-summary-element","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"html.elements.summary"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.summary","dataURL":"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/details\"><code>&lt;details&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Attributes","id":"attributes"},{"text":"Usage notes","id":"usage_notes"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"HTML 공개 요약 요소 (<요약>) 요소는 (\"상세\") 요소의 공개 상자에 대한 요약, 캡션 또는 범례를 지정한다. ","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<summary>: The Disclosure Summary element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<summary> : l'élément de révélation d'un résumé","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<summary>: 概要明示要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"summary","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"<summary>: The Disclosure Summary element","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<summary>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"<summary>","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/html/element/summary","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/html/element/summary/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: Hypertext Markup Language"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"HTML 요소 참고서"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary","title":"<summary>"}],"pageTitle":"<summary> - HTML: Hypertext Markup Language | MDN","noIndexing":false}}